  <main>
    <section identifier="/ca-mountain-view/chapter-1/article-i/section-sec.-1.1"
             temporalId="sSEC_ 1_1">
      <num>SEC. 1.1</num>
      <heading>How code designated and cited</heading>
      <content>
        <p>The ordinances embraced in the following chapters and sections shall constitute and
               be designated &quot;The Code of the City of Mountain View, California,&quot; and may be so cited.
               Such code may also be cited as the &quot;Mountain View City Code.&quot;</p>
        <p>(Code 1938, Sec. 1.)</p>
      </content>
    </section>
  </main>
